# Read Me

This repository has scripts tha allow for the easy download of different versions of the hashicorp tools in linux.

if the zenity dialog tool is installed, it will pop up a GUI dialog and allow selecting versions of the tools from the dialog.

Example:

```sh
usage: get-terraform.sh [Options] [VERSION]

   Download and install a version of terraform

   -h          : display this help
   -l          : list versions
   -L          : latest version
   -p          : destination path to install

```
